  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/9209893346199bec7e16733255852ca4.avif?t=1627141397\" width=616 height=78 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A brief note from the developers:</h2>The game will still undergo many changes in mechanics and visuals, we count on your feedback to make the game more and more profitable.<br><br><br>Rhythm Race is a rhythm game with different songs in a setting mixed with futurism, neon and synth wave. In it, you will compete against legends of the futuristic race and do your best to win.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 20 songs in quick play mode with 3 difficulty levels.<br></li><li> Playable tutorial mode to learn how to play quickly.<br></li><li> Options menu to remap the keyboard keys</li></ul><br>To play you use the Q W E R T Y keys to change the selected color. Circular dots require you to use the action button (Space Bar)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/be230455371cbbab660d6a8f53a1ac61.poster.avif?t=1627141397\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/be230455371cbbab660d6a8f53a1ac61.webm?t=1627141397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/be230455371cbbab660d6a8f53a1ac61.mp4?t=1627141397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In the continuous arrows you need to be in the correct color and press the action button at the beginning of the path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/386bb97149b144e77a9b20c0ed97fb94.poster.avif?t=1627141397\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/386bb97149b144e77a9b20c0ed97fb94.webm?t=1627141397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/386bb97149b144e77a9b20c0ed97fb94.mp4?t=1627141397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/9209893346199bec7e16733255852ca4.avif?t=1627141397\" width=616 height=78 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A brief note from the developers:</h2>The game will still undergo many changes in mechanics and visuals, we count on your feedback to make the game more and more profitable.<br><br><br>Rhythm Race is a rhythm game with different songs in a setting mixed with futurism, neon and synth wave. In it, you will compete against legends of the futuristic race and do your best to win.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 20 songs in quick play mode with 3 difficulty levels.<br></li><li> Playable tutorial mode to learn how to play quickly.<br></li><li> Options menu to remap the keyboard keys</li></ul><br>To play you use the Q W E R T Y keys to change the selected color. Circular dots require you to use the action button (Space Bar)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/be230455371cbbab660d6a8f53a1ac61.poster.avif?t=1627141397\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/be230455371cbbab660d6a8f53a1ac61.webm?t=1627141397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/be230455371cbbab660d6a8f53a1ac61.mp4?t=1627141397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In the continuous arrows you need to be in the correct color and press the action button at the beginning of the path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298310/extras/386bb97149b144e77a9b20c0ed97fb94.poster.avif?t=1627141397\" width=544 height=3